                    <span>I loved book Sojourner truth. And I think Sojourner it is the best book I have read! I think Sojourner Truth was a fearless character    Sojourner Truth was a slave because she was black.  One day Sojourner Truth escaped.  The man found her but he could not get her.  And when she grew up the man sold her son.  SO they went to court and won! She also  had  great courage. Be sure to read this great book!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great photographs and text reveal a different way of life.</div>
